OL,3,C'Grief will not define' soldier's
OL,4,Cparents as they launch anti-bullying
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FCallum's parents speak to ITV News'
OL,8,FSam Blackledge about grief, pride and
OL,9,Ftheir hope for the future.
OL,11,FThe parents of a Cornish man who was
OL,12,Fkilled while volunteering for the
OL,13,FUkrainian army say they "will not let
OL,14,Fgrief define them" and are launching
OL,15,Fan anti-bullying campaign in his
OL,16,Fmemory.
OL,18,FCallum Tindal-Draper was 22 when he
OL,19,Flost his life serving with the foreign
OL,20,Fvolunteer platoon against Russia, last
OL,21,Fmonth.
