OL,3,C'Grief will not define' soldier's
OL,4,Cparents as they launch anti-bullying
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FHis parents, Steven and Caroline, said
OL,8,Fthey tried to persuade him not travel
OL,9,Fto Ukraine.
OL,11,F"Obviously we didn't want him to go,
OL,12,Fbut he was adamant," Caroline said.
OL,13,F"In the end, after a lot of heart and
OL,14,Fsoul searching - it wasn't an
OL,15,Fovernight decision, it was many years
OL,16,Fof us trying to persuade him not to go
OL,17,F- we sat down, we listened to him, and
OL,18,Fwe said we agree with you.
OL,20,F"And actually if we were in your time
OL,21,Fnow, we would do exactly the same."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
