OL,3,C'Grief will not define' soldier's
OL,4,Cparents as they launch anti-bullying
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FSteven added: "On the morning he left,
OL,8,Fwe had a huge hug and I said 'Callum,
OL,9,Fthere are a million other things I'd
OL,10,Frather you do, but I am so proud of
OL,11,Fwhat you're doing, so proud.'"
OL,13,FAs a teenager, Callum was badly
OL,14,Fbullied. His parents say this went a
OL,15,Flong way towards shaping his future.
OL,17,F"The outcome of that was that he vowed
OL,18,Fhe would never ever be bullied again,"
OL,19,FSteven said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
