OL,3,C'Grief will not define' soldier's
OL,4,Cparents as they launch anti-bullying
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,F"That went beyond just school circles
OL,8,Fand he started to look at what's going
OL,9,Fon in the world and he started to
OL,10,Fquestion 'Why are countries allowed to
OL,11,Fbully other countries?'"
OL,13,FCaroline and Steven are raising money
OL,14,Ffor a charity called 'Bullies Out',
OL,15,Fwhich aims to empower and inspire
OL,16,Fchildren.
OL,18,FCaroline said: "We decided we weren't
OL,19,Fgoing to let grief define us. We are
OL,20,Factually going to celebrate and
OL,21,Fembrace life.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
